{hbase.version}
&lt;p&gt; instead of 0.92.x.  The proper method to control version number is to use Versions Maven Plugin.  see: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mojo.codehaus.org/versions-maven-plugin/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://mojo.codehaus.org/versions-maven-plugin/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch should be reverted.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
